There is strong evidence that the moderator of this group is still
very much alive.  Right now, he is between semesters and is trying to
finish cleaning his house up.  When he gets through that project, he
plans on keeping some promises made to a college professor regarding
overdue programming assignments as well as revise the code for Jesse,
mainly create an assistant program for Jesse and change out code to
eliminate the need for calling several functions as well as make the
program more flexible for changes in the source code for gladiator. 
Once those new changes are implemented in Jesse, specs will change. 
For once, Jesse will actually require at least 1 data file be
installed in the same folder as the rest of the program.  To do the
stuff he really wants to do, you'll also have to have a copy of the
graphic files for gladiator installed in the same folder as Jesse, at
least for this version.

;)
